I am going to suggest a new security strategy that will enable us to achieve that goal.
Before such statements, Mr. Peña Nieto's political career as governor of his native state of Mexico City had progressed alongside the President of the United States.
In his home country, in a densely populous and vast state surrounding the capital, opinions about the new leader were divided.
Direct person
