It is very direct and very committed to the realization of its vision for the future of the country.
He's an excellent statesman, and above all, a man who can listen.
But in the other part of the state, many people have a different idea of the former governor.
The Nesaualcoyotl city, also known as Ciudad Nessa, is the most striking contrast to the paved streets of Valle de Bravo.
Hidden under motorways, it is in many ways a suburb of Mexico City itself.
And the problems in the city are also the severity of this mega-city.
